THE Red Ants are in mourning after a member was shot and stabbed to death on Friday and two others were seriously injured. The violent incident happened as the Red Ants were removing people from land next to a railway in Waterworks squatter camp, near Lenasia in Joburg. The situation turned deadly after furious residents started protesting and attacking the Red Ants. if(typeof za24_DisplayAd != "undefined") za24_DisplayAd("300x250","2");var viewReq = new Array();function vu(u) {var i=new Image();i.src=u.replace("&amp;","&");viewReq.push(i);}vu("https://securepubads.g.doubleclick.net/pcs/view?xai\x3dAKAOjstJFGxPoCR_FByAnxwnj-ICnZPT4mFZF9w8jkQ3tHeF-shuzAx2k1gc2Ha7hEuTXowa2srF9P4lYNlsYuoTqelwsZ8bC8qIYpcwc8Jc9nA1bbDdg8Xs9QkUdhoWrALDC9mtSvb96j4HOmm2O69bvrdQAU6eSkE-k7STMjLPK2jw3JyjzvRrziaxr8brUnLxSe2HIuwjXa0vZDIrSOHOufu-EcpXVS-sa6iWAELAZK4GX8pcwQS1xyBQipdwUjUhKpwYt8S2hlwf9VE9Ai9hC8OLlmzJeTo\x26sig\x3dCg0ArKJSzNVd1bcvAuf_EAE\x26urlfix\x3d1\x26adurl\x3d")

   
